title: AC-DC - Boston Tea Party (Bonus Live 2-CD) 1978-81 ak320
description:
AC-DC - Boston Tea Party (Bonus Live 2-CD) 1978 ak320

Boston, Paradise Theater Aug. 21st 1978 This is the date of the main show the 2nd Disc is a group of 4 tracks that they did in 1981 in Boston but I could not quite figure out the gig. 
It was from but they sounded so good that I was not gonna just let them sit idle in my hdd.

 I found em on a different site and when I got em they were FLAC. So enjoy The Boston Tea Party and the Bonus Shots LOL
So Its Brian and Bon no Axl
(Update: Im learning more about the 1981 show maybe I get the complete gig)

Tracklist  Disk 1

01 - WBCN Radio Intro.mp3
02 - Live Wire.mp3
03 - Problem Child.mp3
04 - Sin City.mp3
05 - Gone Shootin'.mp3
06 - Bad Boy Boogie.mp3
07 - The Jack.mp3
08 - High Voltage.mp3
09 - Rocker.mp3
10 - Bon Interview.mp3
11 - Dog Eat Dog.mp3
12 - WBCN Radio Outro.mp3

Bonus Disk 2 Tracklist

01. Back in Black(Bonus).mp3
02. Bad BoyBoogie(Bonus).mp3
03. Rock'n'Roll Ain't Noise Pollution(Bonus).mp3
04. Guitar Solo(Bonus).mp3

Players 1978 

Bon Scott -  Lead Vocals(died 1980) 
Angus Young - Lead Guitar
Malcolm Young - Rhythm Guitar
Cliff Williams - Bass
Phil Rudd - Drums

1981

Angus Young - Lead Guitar
Malcolm Young - Rhythm Guitar
Brian Johnson - Lead Vocals
Cliff Williams - Bass
Phil Rudd - Drums
